location: 90 Dock St, Victoria, BC V8V 2A1, V9A 0G2
description: Join this drop-in social event featuring a 2 hr 30 min session. Recurring on Wednesdays (26 Mar, 2 Apr, 9 Apr, 16 Apr). Come practice your zouk! New dancers are welcome. Enjoy a shared warm up, exchange knowledge, and dance. Entrance is via the side door with stairs down from the parking lot.
